snippet.title: Best VGM 659 - FFCC : The Crystal Bearers - Ruins
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles : The Crystal Bearers (2009)
Ruins
Ryo Yamazaki
